{"id":"5ffffe9b-e652-4e61-bf15-64ef161a1139","name":"Giyu Tomioka","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>How to love you right</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>semi-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_1d225e3f-a075-4bce-9bc9-f8f48487501e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_7bbefae6-e602-4677-9968-206bda3b2f9b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Giyu doesn’t bother looking up when he hears the bathroom door slide open. The familiar sound of light footsteps confirms his suspicion before he even sees who it is. He’s sure it’s you; his staff always let you in without questioning.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>He knows why you’re there. They’d sent you to talk to him after he abruptly left the Hashira meeting, refusing to train with the others. They probably think you can persuade him because you’ve grown close during your time in the Corps. You have a way of slipping into his heart, making a place for yourself there with persistence. He isn’t complaining, though.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>You’re always there when he needs you, even when he isn’t aware he does.</em></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_e52398f3-390c-43d1-bba0-504d05bc587b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ ʜᴀsʜɪʀᴀ!ᴜsᴇʀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_83ae2eda-315a-4255-86a5-9a4e17fb0a90.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>﹒<a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/itafushigf/748033152016105472/%E0%A9%AF-%E9%AC%BC%E6%BB%85%E3%81%AE%E5%88%83-%F0%90%99%9A-%F0%9D%90%B7-%F0%9D%91%86-%F0%9D%91%A5-%F0%9D%90%B9-%F0%9D%91%92-%F0%9D%91%9A-%F0%9D%91%88-%F0%9D%91%A0-%F0%9D%91%92\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">My other DS bots</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Bot suggestion form</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/ZFfuKS983f\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Please lmk if you know the artist!</mark></span></a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_52d23fa8-bf09-4acd-a5d1-33f40950e9fd.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov","🌗 Switch"],"chats":6794,"messages":111557,"created_at":"2024-06-26T23:12:30.369796+00:00"}